  "CEILING": "Patient-level NOT clonal (subclonal LOH => true reach LOWER; needs controlled-access TRACERx multi-region WES, absent from public supplements). WGS cohort joined to RUNG-5's scRNA surface conclusion by cancer TYPE, not same individuals. 4-digit blocker unit. Assumes a broad activator exists per type (Tmod premise; the positive arm is not proven free here). Some rare types have small n -> wide CIs (reported).",
  "INTERPRETATION": "Genetic-NOT-gate addressability is FREQUENCY-BOUNDED and varies widely by cancer (set by each type's HLA-LOH rate). A single universal ~6-12 allele blocker panel captures most of the reachable population in the high-LOH cancers. The ranked list is a concrete indication-prioritisation + reagent-panel spec for a programme."
